If you create a new language, remember to complete the following steps:

1) Create a suitable language directory under po with the official language
   code, e.g. "fr" for French

2)

…

n) Create a file named after your language code with "config" appended, e.g.
   fr.config for French in scripts

n+1) Include the following lines updated for your language (this example uses
   the hypothetical case of English):
langcode="en"
langname="English"
langname_translated="English"
hint1=", "
hint2="translations are missing until 80%"

n+2) copy and adapt license.add, translate-dates.pl and generate-addendum.sh

n+3) In public, create …
